---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Juan Pablo Palomo"
  description="Estudiante de Ingeniería Empresarial en UFM. Automatización de procesos, análisis de datos e inteligencia artificial."
  ogDescription="Business Engineering student at UFM. Process automation, data analysis, and artificial intelligence."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <div class="cv-hero-wrap">
    <section class="cv-hero">
      <div class="cv-hero__text">
        <h1 class="cv-hero__name">Juan Pablo<br />Palomo</h1>
        <div class="cv-hero__sub">
          <span class="es">Ingeniería Empresarial</span>
          <span class="en">Business Engineering</span>
          <span class="cv-hero__dot">·</span>
          <span>Guatemala</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="cv-hero__avatar">
        <img src="/foto.png" alt="Juan Pablo Palomo" />
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <!-- CV sections -->
  <div class="container--wide">

    <!-- Perfil -->
    <div class="cv-section">
      <span class="cv-section__label">
        <span class="es">Perfil</span>
        <span class="en">Profile</span>
      </span>
      <div class="cv-section__content">
        <p class="cv-profile es">
          Estudiante apasionado por la automatización de procesos, análisis de datos e inteligencia artificial,
          con habilidades avanzadas en Excel (certificación Microsoft Excel Expert), programación en R, Python y VBA,
          y conocimientos sólidos en contabilidad. Experiencia desarrollando soluciones para optimizar flujos de
          trabajo y automatizar reportes.
        </p>
        <p class="cv-profile en">
          Passionate student of process automation, data analysis, and artificial intelligence,
          with advanced skills in Excel (Microsoft Excel Expert certification), programming in R, Python, and VBA,
          and solid knowledge of accounting. Experienced in developing solutions to optimize workflows and automate reports.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Experiencia -->
    <div class="cv-section">
      <span class="cv-section__label">
        <span class="es">Experiencia</span>
        <span class="en">Experience</span>
      </span>
      <div class="cv-section__content">

        <div class="cv-entry">
          <div class="cv-entry__title">
            <span class="es">Freelance — Automatización y Análisis de Datos</span>
            <span class="en">Freelance — Automation & Data Analysis</span>
          </div>
          <div class="cv-entry__sub">
            <span class="es">Autónomo</span>
            <span class="en">Self-employed</span>
          </div>
          <div class="cv-entry__date">
            2023 — <span class="es">Actualidad</span><span class="en">Present</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="cv-entry__list">
            <li>
              <span class="es">Automatización de reportes periódicos usando macros y scripts en Python/R.</span>
              <span class="en">Automated periodic reports using macros and scripts in Python/R.</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="es">Limpieza y transformación de grandes volúmenes de datos para análisis operativo.</span>
              <span class="en">Data cleaning and transformation of large datasets for operational analysis.</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="es">Aplicación de IA para clasificar, analizar y presentar información relevante.</span>
              <span class="en">Applied AI to classify, analyze, and present relevant information.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="cv-entry">
          <div class="cv-entry__title">
            <span class="es">Venta de Fruta de Temporada — Gestión de Operaciones</span>
            <span class="en">Seasonal Fruit Sales — Operations Management</span>
          </div>
          <div class="cv-entry__sub">
            <span class="es">Negocio Familiar</span>
            <span class="en">Family Business</span>
          </div>
          <div class="cv-entry__date">2023, 2024, 2025</div>
          <ul class="cv-entry__list">
            <li>
              <span class="es">Coordinación de operaciones de venta al menudeo durante campañas de temporada.</span>
              <span class="en">Coordinated retail sales operations during seasonal campaigns.</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="es">Implementación de sistema de control de inventarios y ventas en Excel y WebApps con Python.</span>
              <span class="en">Implemented an inventory and sales control system using Excel and Python WebApps.</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="es">Liderazgo de equipo.</span>
              <span class="en">Team leadership.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Educación -->
    <div class="cv-section">
      <span class="cv-section__label">
        <span class="es">Educación</span>
        <span class="en">Education</span>
      </span>
      <div class="cv-section__content">

        <div class="cv-entry">
          <div class="cv-entry__title">Universidad Francisco Marroquín</div>
          <div class="cv-entry__sub">
            <span class="es">Licenciatura en Ingeniería Empresarial</span>
            <span class="en">Business Engineering Bachelor's Degree</span>
          </div>
          <div class="cv-entry__date">
            2024 — <span class="es">actualidad</span><span class="en">present</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="cv-entry">
          <div class="cv-entry__title">APDE, El Roble</div>
          <div class="cv-entry__sub">
            <span class="es">Primaria, básicos y diversificado</span>
            <span class="en">International Baccalaureate</span>
          </div>
          <div class="cv-entry__date">2013 — 2023</div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Habilidades -->
    <div class="cv-section">
      <span class="cv-section__label">
        <span class="es">Habilidades</span>
        <span class="en">Skills</span>
      </span>
      <div class="cv-section__content">
        <div class="cv-skills">

          <div class="cv-skill">
            <div>
              <div class="cv-skill__name">Excel Avanzado</div>
            </div>
            <div class="cv-skill__desc">
              <span class="es">Tablas dinámicas, macros, validaciones, automatización de reportes.</span>
              <span class="en">Pivot tables, macros, validations, report automation.</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="cv-skill">
            <div>
              <div class="cv-skill__name">
                <span class="es">Programación</span>
                <span class="en">Programming</span>
              </div>
              <div class="cv-skill__sub">Python · R · VBA</div>
            </div>
            <div class="cv-skill__desc">
              <span class="es">Automatización, optimización de procesos, manejo y análisis de datos, webapps, visualización.</span>
              <span class="en">Automation, process optimization, data handling and analysis, webapps, visualization.</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="cv-skill">
            <div>
              <div class="cv-skill__name">
                <span class="es">Contabilidad</span>
                <span class="en">Accounting</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cv-skill__desc">
              <span class="es">Registros contables, estados financieros, contabilidad de costos. Conocimiento financiero básico.</span>
              <span class="en">Accounting records, financial statements, cost accounting. Basic financial knowledge.</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="cv-skill">
            <div>
              <div class="cv-skill__name">
                <span class="es">Inteligencia Artificial</span>
                <span class="en">Artificial Intelligence</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cv-skill__desc">
              <span class="es">Aplicación de IA para resolución de problemas y optimización de tareas.</span>
              <span class="en">Applying AI for problem solving and task optimization.</span>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Contacto -->
    <div class="cv-section">
      <span class="cv-section__label">
        <span class="es">Contacto</span>
        <span class="en">Contact</span>
      </span>
      <div class="cv-section__content">
        <div class="cv-contact">
          <a href="mailto:jppalomo10@gmail.com" class="cv-contact__item">
            jppalomo10@gmail.com
          </a>
          <span class="cv-contact__item">Guatemala, Guatemala</span>
          <span class="cv-contact__item">LinkedIn — Juan Pablo Palomo García</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>
